{"tid":2291068,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"夫婦鬧交點火燒對方，宏景花園低層單位起火","createTime":"2020-11-18T13:06:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T15:48:13.000Z","uid":38539,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"3f19c409f755cac5c02e31a525f5e7c4782851a4","tid":2291068,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:06:20.000Z","msg":"鑽石山發生火警。傍晚6時許，警方接獲報告指宏景花園1座低層一單位起火冒煙，消防到場將火救熄，屋內1男1女臉部燒傷，需敷上面膜送院救治，其中女戶主情況比較嚴重，正調查起火原因。事件中，30人需要疏散至安全位置，現場消息指，涉事兩人為夫婦關係，事發時二人發生爭執，有人情緒激動，之後點火燒向對方，未幾另一人亦告受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201118/2OL34Z3MKBCVJNEGKIBB7G3UWE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201118%2F2OL34Z3MKBCVJNEGKIBB7G3UWE%2F&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5kxj1a1M9JfR6d2dSWReNkw%3D&h=9972929c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201118%2F2OL34Z3MKBCVJNEGKIBB7G3UWE%2F&h=35305b2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201118/2OL34Z3MKBCVJNEGKIBB7G3UWE/</a>"},{"pid":"0eac59e5422788cafb784e416454634ed1107e96","tid":2291068,"uid":38737,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:10:07.000Z","msg":"火魔法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2898bbcbd5e84bcc6b55db34f60edbd2a65a9259","tid":2291068,"uid":208940,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:10:22.000Z","msg":"咁撚殘忍互燒對方，為何要結婚?"},{"pid":"8260302051d3f920391e9f8be0a86306ac5cdf86","tid":2291068,"uid":109050,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:11:11.000Z","msg":"愛人變仇人"},{"pid":"5d7fab2895fdfb3be3d4f061de8f2973fb60bb2d","tid":2291068,"uid":38539,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2898bbcbd5e84bcc6b55db34f60edbd2a65a9259","tid":2291068,"uid":208940,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:10:22.000Z","msg":"咁撚殘忍互燒對方，為何要結婚?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:11:34.000Z"